name: #21 - YU
description: 2013 - A large part of what I produced on the streets was left behind. Only kept in the memory of those who can observe them while they were alive in the streets. Based on this reflection of time, ephemerality and memories, I decided to transform into NFT some photographs that still remain from that time, which is very special to me. I've been on the streets since 2008 and this is one of the strands of art in which I manifest myself.
